
When adding code review to a project. 

Step 1 – Select the project. 



Step 2 – Click on “Setting” at the top of the window. 



Step 3 – On the left side of the screen click “Branches”



Step 4 – Click Add rule



Step 5 – Enter the branch name you want to add the code review too. 



Step 6 – Check the box “Require pull request reviews before merging” leave the required approving review: 1.  Then check the box “Restrict who can dismiss pull request reviews”.  Add the users that will be able to override pull request.



Step 7 – Create the create button at the bottom of the page.

 
